            <title>[LU-15533] (md_object.h:399:lu2md()) ASSERTION( o == ((void *)0) || IS_ERR(o) || lu_device_is_md(o-&gt;lo_dev) ) failed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15533</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are still on disk objects whose FIDs cause the fid2path handler to panic. For example the &lt;tt&gt;OI_scrub&lt;/tt&gt; file. In the past we have inserted various tests on fids to try to avoid this. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It would be better if mdt_object_find() simply never returned such objects.&lt;/p&gt;

